Class CompactBNodeTurtleWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openrdf.rio.helpers.RDFWriterBase
      • org.openrdf.rio.turtle.TurtleWriter
        • eu.semagrow.hibiscus.util.CompactBNodeTurtleWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openrdf.rio.RDFHandler, org.openrdf.rio.RDFWriter

    public class CompactBNodeTurtleWriter
extends org.openrdf.rio.turtle.TurtleWriter
    Writes compact turtle syntax using the [] shorthand notation if a BNode occurs as object in a triple statement followed by triple statements with the same BNode in subject position. Beware: if the [] syntax is applied the BNode MUST occur in consecutive triple statements. Otherwise, the link between individual statement groups would be lost due to the omission of the the BNode ID.
    Author:
    Olaf Goerlitz
